description:
THE UCHRONIC SERIES WITH MEKAPANZERS INSIDE!

How will the appearance of a new technology in 1944 alter the course of World War II? And how will this lead the Axis towards Victory?

1946: the Mecha War begins!

1936. In the midst of a Europe which has been at peace for 75 years, a new city ermerges unlike any other in the world: Metropolis, the capital of excess and urban delirium. It is the focal point of numerous political movements and artistic trends as well as the nerve center for various forms of espionage and other underhanded activities. The citizens of Metropolis speak of nothing else but the horrible crimes plaguing the poorest parts of the city. To solve these crimes, the police have called upon an Austrian doctor, the inventor of a little-known field of science involving the treatment of the mind: a certain Doctor Freud.

Face-to-face with Camille, can Anthony do what he set out to do, or will he become another victim? Are the Puppets able to help their new Master… or does Camille still have some pull with the stringless Puppets?

description: Marriage is on everyone's mind at Bayside High, when the students must pair up for a "married couple" budget assignment. When fake money is tight, tensions run high! How can feminist Jessie and chauvinist Slater make their marriage work? Will Lisa blow her entire budget on shoes? Will Screech be stuck as a bachelor forever? One thing's for sure: Zack's got to impress Kelly by being such a great fake husband, she'll want to be his REAL girlfriend!

CJ continues her desperate search for her daughter, now more certain than ever that she is still alive. As she travels deeper and deeper into the desert, and closer to the mysterious evil known as Rush Bridge, the forces of terror gather all around her. To be granted an audience with the meth-cult-leader Rush Bridge, one must be "marked." But to know what it means to be marked one must possess the courage to make it all the way through the nightmare known as Sunflower #3. Good luck keeping your eyes open.

... Are Often Deceiving

Selene's true motives and loyalties come to light, and the Torchbearers have found new actionable intel in their fight against the corporations.
name: ... Are Often Deceiving

description:
Supernatural bounty hunter John Tower has long been a man shrouded in mystery. Now, discover what set him on this path of horror as his origins are finally uncovered, revealing just what Tower is risking his life to find!

Alicia's new ally, an apostate of the Brotherhood of the Rose, attracts unwanted attention, sending them on the run. Questioning his methods, Tower realizes his search requires the skill of a detective, not the force of a hunter.

In the summer of 1946, the Japanese have been beaten but World War II continues in Europe after the Normandy landings failed on June 6th, 1944.

Completely revolutionary jet planes, the Wunderwaffen, or Wonder Weapons, now efficiently defend Germany. Major Walter Murnau, a man of honor and talented Wunderwaffen pilot, finds himself decorated by Adolf Hitler. Nicknamed The Devil's Pilot, he becomes the icon of something he despises. But even for him, Hell is not that far away, as he's facing enemies from outside and from inside his own country...
name: The Gates of Hell 2/2

description:
